{"tid":2442303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵去年虧蝕48.09億元","createTime":"2021-03-11T09:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T09:54:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b955ef89850fa42346cc7c44f8dc4a5ab5c295e7","tid":2442303,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"早前已經發盈警的港鐵(00066)公布, 去年業績由盈轉虧, 虧損48億零900萬元, 是上市以來業績首度見紅, 對上年度就錄得盈利119億3200萬元, 但仍然派發末期息每股98仙, 全年派息維持在1.32元.<br />\n        業績錄得虧損, 主要由於投資物業重估錄得91億9千萬元的虧損, 但經常性業務亦都錄得虧損11億2600萬元, 至於物業發展利潤就微跌百分之1.3, 至55億零700萬元.<br />\n        去年乘客量下跌百分之31.5, 而本港客運總乘客人次下跌兩成七, 至11億4500萬人次, 本港客運業務連續兩年錄得虧損, 去年虧損擴大至54億元. 另外, 商場、免稅店、其他車站商店及車站廣告業務均受到不利影響, 車站商務息稅前利潤下跌五成一, 至25億元.<br />\n        期內, 本港客運業務收入下跌四成, 至近119億元, 至於車站商務收入亦下跌五成二, 至32億6900萬元.<br />\n        公司指, 疫情發展仍然不明朗, 對旗下經常性業務不利影響可能會在今年持續.<br />\n        港鐵又指, 日出康城三個項目的利潤入帳會視乎建築進度而定, 而未來一年內會視乎市況, 為四項物業發展項目進行招標, 包括黃竹坑「港島南岸」第六期, 東涌牽引配電站用地、百勝角通風樓用地以及東涌東站第一期.<br />\n        公司指, 去年高鐵香港段項目管理費收入合共65億4800萬元.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20210311164406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20210311164406&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=f290e374\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20210311164406</a>"},{"pid":"eeed153cc67587d5ce9e4e110dff1cf986d01b82","tid":2442303,"uid":45572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:23:26.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 無人搭仲要請minion捉人"},{"pid":"f6e2ef527abe4b28cf20592974a41060dc41b47f","tid":2442303,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"日日都捉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最on9"},{"pid":"fa558b8ef09d397fc919780c6fd0b37e58487ca3","tid":2442303,"uid":267283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"運輸方面近乎壟斷<br />\n都可以蝕到咁<br />\n<br />\n真垃圾"},{"pid":"1faeecbd3bccd08bae5bfd2c40ca9cdcf4abd926","tid":2442303,"uid":393145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"想搭吓車都俾5 6個黃衫人迫埋牆角, 又兇又搜又盛, 搵鬼搭咩"},{"pid":"9f77e891594f07eb91bedbcb39e9a2b98e478ce7","tid":2442303,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"解散左CSPRU 可以慳返一億！"},{"pid":"329ff4b2e62abf022f89b7ec2be3f632801394f4","tid":2442303,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"721 831<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d72261708dd0afd107657adf064bfe460c6ee81","tid":2442303,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"羅湖站果條大水喉GG"},{"pid":"d7463ca48d7868ec78930656df6bae90712b51a6","tid":2442303,"uid":20870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:35:33.000Z","msg":"物業估值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa190102b4f938f49cb6965ef1efcc5694eacf7e","tid":2442303,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d72261708dd0afd107657adf064bfe460c6ee81","tid":2442303,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"羅湖站果條大水喉GG"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:36:51.000Z","msg":"仲有果條城際直通車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18af9b39126adee5983d66549a57417090a8995d","tid":2442303,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d72261708dd0afd107657adf064bfe460c6ee81","tid":2442303,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"羅湖站果條大水喉GG"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"無左2個關口收入 又唔敢屌大陸放毒搞到全世界經濟變差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2370c8dd8921c1438b239494339c2e0fc1c2fedc","